message: I'm a colored guy who found an American partner and opened a business in the USA. I brought in the investment and I start wondering what is happening in the country. I fear a little bit for myself too. I just see a lot of hatred, racism, xenophobia and bigotry. I find that Trump has got into the minds of even good people that I know. I have had to rethink my plans for the future. God help America if Trump is elected, but in my heart I feel he won't win.
